$OpenBSD: patch-stats_c,v 1.11 2020/04/16 06:54:41 ratchov Exp $

If devinfo.type != AUDIO_MIXER_CLASS is true, xstatbar will never make
progress and loop forever. Fix it by trying the next device.

Index: stats.c
